    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在《幽暗森林里的糖果屋》试玩版中：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟着双主角，安瑟尔与葛蕾塔，一同体验故事的开端——<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/30f42a97c28ae40147cd86f1c1db37e0.poster.avif?t=1770600210\" width=798 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/30f42a97c28ae40147cd86f1c1db37e0.webm?t=1770600210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/30f42a97c28ae40147cd86f1c1db37e0.mp4?t=1770600210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索糖果屋，苹果派厨房、棉花糖玩具房、蛋糕大厅⋯⋯在不同风格的甜点房间，收集独特的食谱与食材。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/127a4507b3165008cec843815eeebd18.poster.avif?t=1770600210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/127a4507b3165008cec843815eeebd18.webm?t=1770600210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/127a4507b3165008cec843815eeebd18.mp4?t=1770600210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用亲手制作的甜点，来解开糖果屋中的各种谜题。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/083f33ec90370b881f779fc83d9fc4e5.poster.avif?t=1770600210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/083f33ec90370b881f779fc83d9fc4e5.webm?t=1770600210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/083f33ec90370b881f779fc83d9fc4e5.mp4?t=1770600210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诡异的洋娃娃、任性的泰迪玩偶、神秘的姜饼双子⋯⋯与神秘的角色相遇并互动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/90463e6631fea835141038a585ac1c3d.poster.avif?t=1770600210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/90463e6631fea835141038a585ac1c3d.webm?t=1770600210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132260/extras/90463e6631fea835141038a585ac1c3d.mp4?t=1770600210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满童话色彩、悬疑又可爱的糖果屋中度过约30～45分钟。</p></li></ul>",
